org.cloudgraph.hbase.io

Class GraphTableReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.state.GraphTable
      • org.cloudgraph.hbase.io.GraphTableReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TableOperation, TableReader, TableState

    public class GraphTableReader
extends GraphTable
implements TableReader
    The operational, configuration and other state information required for read operations on a single graph table.

    Acts as a container for one or more RowReader elements and encapsulates the HBase client Get operations for use in read operations across one or more graph rows.

    Since:
    0.5.1
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    RowReader
